  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "• Explored joint learning of several pre-training tasks to integrate syntax parsing and semantic feature parsing, which are very helpful for forming the Opinion Tree structure.",
    "Hu et al. (2022) argued that the existing methods PARAPHRASE by Zhang et al. (2021a) that used a fixed template order to generate the target sequence are suboptimal because different orders may provide different views of the quadruplet.",
    "ACOSQE is not a conventional generation task, and it is not necessary to fix the element order of the quadruplet as long as it can be accurately extracted.",
    "So, a novel data augmentation method for the task of ACOSQE was introduced.",
    "The proposed method leverages the order-free property of quadruples."
  ],
